 tracks with laps, speed boosts, and a leaderboard",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptGame2"},{shortPrompt:"3D maze game",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptGame3Short",prompt:"A first-person 3D maze game where players collect hidden items while avoiding obstacles and earning points",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptGame3"}]},n={[t.AssetRequestKind.OTHER_OUTPUT_KIND_DOCUMENT]:[{shortPrompt:"Mobile app proposal",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument1Short",prompt:"A project proposal for launching a new mobile app feature, including goals, timeline, resources, and budget",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument1"},{shortPrompt:"Messaging feature PRD",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument2Short",prompt:"A product requirements document for a messaging feature in a collaboration app, outlining user stories and technical requirements",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument2"},{shortPrompt:"Meeting notes template",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument3Short",prompt:"A meeting notes template for startup team meetings with sections for agenda items, decisions, and action items",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptDocument3"}],[t.AssetRequestKind.OTHER_OUTPUT_KIND_SPREADSHEET]:[{shortPrompt:"Student budget tracker",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet1Short",prompt:"A personal monthly budget tracker for a college student with spending categories and budget variance",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet1"},{shortPrompt:"Sales pipeline tracker",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet2Short",prompt:"A sales pipeline tracker for a small B2B startup with deal owners, stages, and expected close dates",promptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet2"},{shortPrompt:"Hiring tracker",shortPromptIntlId:"createRepl.oldExamplePromptSpreadsheet3Short",prompt:"A hiring tracker for a growing startup to track candidates, interview 